{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Relic Abyss is an action-filled anomaly that mixes lovecraftian fantasy with medieval sci-fi, bundled in a cute art-style and a banger soundtrack!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/About_Loop.gif?t=1737543278\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a desolate yet beautiful world being consumed by the Abyss. Embark on a quest to preserve existence, meeting fellow adventurers along the way! Discover ancient relics, forge powerful gear, and evolve your skills to defeat primal evil and prevent catastrophe!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83e\uddd9\u200d\u2640\ufe0f<strong>Play up to 20 uniquely designed adventurers</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/Character_Select.png?t=1737543278\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> \ud83d\udd25<strong>Over 134+ Unique Character Skills including Ultimate Skills</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/Arrow_Rain.gif?t=1737543278\" />\ud83d\udcaa<strong>Choose your own build path</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/Stats.png?t=1737543278\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2692\ufe0f<strong>Upgrade your equipment</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/Smithing.gif?t=1737543278\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udccf<strong>Collect enemy cards and enchant your gear</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/Enchanting.gif?t=1737543278\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udc51<strong>Discover powerful relics</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/Relics.gif?t=1737543278\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\uddfa\ufe0fProcedurally generated levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/Shrines.gif?t=1737543278\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2728<strong>Randomized Perks System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/Perks.gif?t=1737543278\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83e\udd91<strong>Battle otherworldly bosses</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/Boss.gif?t=1737543278\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfd9\ufe0f<strong>City builder elements in an expansive HUB level</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/HUB.png?t=1737543278\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83e\uddd3<strong>Training to improve your abilities</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/Training.gif?t=1737543278\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83e\ude9c<strong>6 Playable Levels with unique encounters</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017760/extras/Levels.gif?t=1737543278\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udc7a<strong>Incremental Difficulty Levels</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=